1	For optimal results, stabilize harvested tissues immediately in RNAlater RNA Stabilization Reagent (see protocol on page 34). Tissues can be stored in the reagent for up to 1 day at 37°C, 7 days at 15–25°C, or 4 weeks at 2–8°C, or archived at –20°C or –80°C.	f	1	2019-05-30 12:40:54.041483	2019-05-30 12:40:54.041483	\N	\N	0
